videos.description: Devontae Shuler makes up for Tigers mistake with a nice steal and slam.
videos.headline: Shuler comes up with heads-up steal and slam

videos.description: Breein Tyree sets up Markel Crawford for an easy layup in transition as the Rebels start off hot.
videos.headline: Crawford finishes after a great drop off from Tyree

videos.description: Mustapha Heron knocks down 3-pointers from each corner for Auburn.
videos.headline: Heron buries back-to-back triples

videos.description: Horace Spencer doesn't give up on the play and pins Devontae Shuler's layup off the backboard.
videos.headline: Spencer pins it off the backboard

videos.description: Mustapha Heron knocks down tough jumper in the face of the defender for the Tigers.
videos.headline: Heron nails step-back jumper

videos.description: Bryce Brown get a layup to go and has scored nine out of the last 13 points for Auburn.
videos.headline: Brown pops off for Auburn late in the 2nd half

videos.description: Terence Davis throws down a vicious slam late against Auburn.
videos.headline: Davis creates a poster of Auburn defender
